      "value": "<p><span id=\"page356R_mcid11\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">The</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">Yuki Clan</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">have access to a separate </span><span dir=\"ltr\">list of Jutsu unique to their Clan. <br />You can add these Jutsu to </span><span dir=\"ltr\">your jutsu list instead of selecting jutsu from the </span><span dir=\"ltr\">Norma</span><span dir=\"ltr\">l jutsu list</span><span dir=\"ltr\">(s). <br />They do not need any Nature </span><span dir=\"ltr\">Release to use their Clan jutsu.</span></span></p>",
